summary: An Ordinance amending Section 4 of Ordinance No. 23523, entitled "An Ordinance relating to official bond to be given by certain officers of the City of Seattle and prescribing the amounts thereof," approved March 15, 1910, as amended by Ordinance No. 24078, approved May 9, 1910, for the purpose of providing that payment of premiums on said bonds shall be paid by the City of Seattle.
